Consider the logic circuit below:

\begin{circuitikz}
\draw
  (0,2) node[and port] (and1) {}
  (0,0) node[not port] (not1) {}
  (and1.in 1) node[left] {A}
  (not1.in) node[left] {B}
  (not1.out) -- (and1.in 2)
  (and1.out) node[right] {Y};
\end{circuitikz}

Complete the truth table for inputs A and B, and output Y.
